Entry Form Checklist

HTML (*-form.component.html)

Wrap related field-group elements in <div class="form-section">.
Add a section label above each group:
<p class="form-section-title">Section Name</p> 2. Typical groupings: Contact Information | Program / Role | Details | Notes. 3. On every required field's label, add the required indicator: <label class="field-label"> Field Name <span class="field-required" aria-hidden="true">*</span> </label> 3. And add the required attribute to the <input> or <select>.
SCSS (*-form.component.scss)

Add:
.form-section { & + & {
margin-top: 8px;
padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--cms-border-light); }
}
.form-section-title {
font-size: 0.6875rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.09em;
